## Regression Policy

1. **Checklist maintenance** — Orchestrator maintains regression checklist in project state from completed P0/P1 tasks.
2. **Trigger** — Any change to shared modules, auth, data layer, or public API triggers affected regression items.
3. **Failure handling** — New failures in previously passing areas → **FAIL**; waivers require orchestrator review and logged decision.
4. **Checkpoint commits** — Risky fixes use checkpoint mode before merge per `core/qa-loop.md`.
5. **Re-QA scope** — After fix loop, re-run full regression on touched areas, not only failed criteria.

