## Security Testing

| Control | Requirement | Command / tool | Frequency | Pass criteria |
|---------|-------------|----------------|-----------|---------------|
| Secrets scan | No committed secrets | `{{SECRETS_SCAN_CMD}}` | Every security-touched task | Zero findings or accepted exceptions in decisions |
| Dependency audit | Known CVEs | `{{DEP_AUDIT_CMD}}` | Each release phase | No unaccepted critical/high |
| Auth / authz | Access control | {{AUTH_TEST_APPROACH}} | Auth changes | Negative tests pass |
| Input fuzzing | Injection resistance | {{FUZZ_APPROACH}} | External input surfaces | No exploitable findings |

Mandatory security review agent: `4-security` when task touches auth, crypto, network egress, or secrets handling.

